Finalmente ci siamo riusciti...
Tutti e otto seduti insieme, allo stesso tavolo, lontano da pressioni e tempistiche lavorative. Il tempo per qualche ora si è fermato in una serata fantastica all’insegna dell’amicizia e di alcuni valori che condividiamo tutti nel miglior modo possibile e cioè l’italianità e l’artigianalità. Un ringraziamento particolare va al brand che ha organizzato tutto nello specifico @tbdeyewear con @fabioattanasio e il @vun_andreaaprea dello chef stellato @andreaaprea_official che ci ha letteralmente deliziato e viziato.
@alessandrosquarzi @filomagno82 @alessandro.roia @leonida @gentlemen_wear_daily @luca_rubinacci ——————————————-
Finally we made it...
All eight sitting together at the same table, away from pressures and working schedules. Time has stopped for a couple hours in a fantastic evening in the name of friendship and some values which we all share in the best way possible which are italianness and craftsmanship. A special thanks goes specifically to a brand which has organized everything @tbdeyewear with @fabioattanasio and @vun_andreaaprea owner of the Michelin star restaurant @andreaaprea_official who literally delighted us
#FrankGallucci #proudtobeitalian #ParkHyatt #tbdeyewear

Cashmere , personally, means a lot of things. It reminds me such a pleasant memories related to my childhood. I used to open up my father’s closet, exploring all his garments and touching with my hands all the fabrics especially knitwear; once my fingers went on cashmere, the first sensation (feeling) was: “wow what an incredible tenderness and such an unbelievable difference with the other fabrics. My father taught me about this noble fiber and what is behind its production process @falconeriofficial  #Falconeri #SuperiorCashmere #Adv #FrankGallucci #proudtobeitalian #MadeInItaly
